Package: PrimerDesigner
Title: CRISPR Primer Design Pipeline for Non-Model Organisms
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jae-Yoon", "Sung", email = "o3wodbs@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2475-8743"))
Description: End-to-end CRISPR primer design pipeline for non-model organisms. Automates BSgenome package building for any NCBI genome, Bowtie index creation, genome-wide gRNA library generation with composite scoring and off-target analysis via CrisprVerse, and cloning primer design (Golden Gate, Gibson Assembly). Includes unified gRNA + deletion arm pipeline with 4-primer Gibson design for homologous recombination knockouts, combined all-in-one construct GenBank output for SnapGene visualization, methylation site filtering, and Tm-optimized primer generation. Works with any organism that has a GenBank accession.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
